 trying like heck to get my faction up for the scout blade quest.  This is requiring me to run the Scout Cape quest a couple of times.  Getting Kelynn to pop can be a trial in and of itself, but if someone else is there and needs to run the quest, I'll gladly step aside, and even help them.<br><br>If on the other hand, I'm running the quest and someone comes up and tells me they're taking the camp, then it's every man for himself and whoever gets him gets him (he depops after you give him the coin, so you have to get him to pop again after each running of the quest).<br><br>This is how it was after EQ came out of beta, at least on Tarew Marr, and frankly I'm supprised that the community has allowed 'camping' and 'farming' to go on as long as it has.  Now we have a nice new server and I'm equally shocked that all of those who are opposed to farming are complaining about 'camp rights'. <p>Fritz Darkweaver<BR>Wood Elven Scout of Tunare<BR><B>1st Fist of Light</B>, emeritus<BR><BR><I>"Rich man, poor man, beggar man, thief" -- E. E. Milne</I></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=55.topic&start=21&stop=21>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=55.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=55.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=55.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=55.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="